            <title><![CDATA[Nintendo Wants Mario To Live Past 100 Years Old]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-wants-mario-to-live-past-100-years-old/1100-6535761/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
